QuestData.Title: Culling the Swarm
QuestData.Description: The Empress continues to amass her forces. Without intervention, they WILL overrun that wall - even if it means smothering it in the corpses of a million swarmborn.$B$BLet us find a better place for those corpses.$B$BLet me know when you are ready to depart for the clutches - I will gladly drop you in from above.
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay 40 Shek'zeer Mantid in the Clutches of Shek'zeer. Speak with Kil'ruk the Wind-Reaver for an air-drop.
